description: The Cookie Monstah is taking the best baked concoctions through all of Boston. Once you try a bite of any of these made-from-scratch treats, you too will be another big fan. Missy Gale took her years of culinary experience, as well as her familial background in baking to solve her search for the perfect cookie. After introducing the locals to her very own fresh batches of Snickerdoodle, Chocolate Chip, M&M;, Red Velvet (and more!), as well as her selection of premium ice cream flavors for impeccable ice cream sandwiches, The Cookie Monstah truck quickly became wicked famous and was even featured on Travel Channel’s Bizarre Foods: Delicious Destinations. These desserts are truly delectable and are an absolute crowd favorite, so when planning your next exciting event, be sure to keep The Cookie Monstah in mind.
name: The Cookie Monstah
